title: The Transport Tote: Corduroy Suede Edition
text:
Product Details

Made of rich Italian suede.

Please note: As it is made of a natural material, each bag varies slightly in texture and color.

Interior pocket.

8 1/4" handle drop.

13 3/4"H x 14"W x 6 1/4"D.

Import.

Madewell.com only.

AA093

What goes into this '70s take on our signature tote? Here it is by the numbers: 2 pieces of corduroy textured Italian suede are used for the body. 8 inch strap drop: long enough to sling over your shoulder, but short enough to hold as a top handle. 1 interior side zip pocket to keep your keys, phone and wallet at the ready. 24: the number of hours in a day that this bag looks cool. How often you'll reach for it? 500 gazillion times.
